data.description: 7 Minutes to the beautiful Navarre Beach!  Assumable VA!  This could be just what you are looking for!  Over 2800 square feet 4 bedrooms 3 bath plus formal dining, office and breakfast nook.  Large family room with wood burning fireplace overlooks nice lania and private large back yard with storage building.  The updated kitchen has abundant cabinet and counter space, soft touch drawers, and a spacious pantry.  The master suite has a trey ceiling and French doors to a ptio.  The bath has a jetted tub, separate shower, double vanity and double closets.  The split bedroom has a bedroom bath on one and 2 bedrooms with bath that also has double vanitys on the front side.  New flooring, Plantation shutters, lighting and fixtures in some rooms.  Located across from the Golf Course.  This home also includes amenities of Holley by the Sea.
